
# Flask Contact App

This is a simple Flask app with the following features:
- Home, About, and Contact pages.
- SQLite database integration for storing contact messages.
- Flash messages for user feedback.

## How to Run

1. Install dependencies:
```bash
   pip install -r requirements.txt
```
   
To make a basic python app/website:

run: 
```bash
python -m venv venv
source venv\Scripts\activate
```
then: 
```bash
pip install flask
```

RUN:
```bash 
run python app.py
```

ROUTES:

Set up Inside app.py

HTML:

Inside templates:
(1) Basic template inside base.html
(2) Main page: index.html

CSS:

Inside /static

## CREATE REUSABLE TEMPLATES

Paste this inside 

```bash
{% extends 'base.html' %}
{% block title %}About{% endblock %}
{% block content %}
    <h2>About My App</h2>
    <p>This is the about page.</p>
{% endblock %}
```

